&lt;h2&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Senior Director of Delivery is the second most senior leadership role in the organization, reporting directly to the Executive Director and serving as a key driver of Imagine Worldwide Sierra Leone’s strategy and impact. This position plays a central role in advancing Imagine’s mission to design, deliver, and scale high-quality tablet-based learning solutions that enable children across Sierra Leone to achieve foundational literacy and numeracy at national scale.&lt;/p&gt;
